05). <i>Steve Wright's Book of Factoids</i>. HarperCollins Entertainment. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-00-720660-7\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-00-720660-7\">0-00-720660-7</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Steve+Wright%27s+Book+of+Factoids&amp;rft.pub=HarperCollins+Entertainment&amp;rft.date=2005&amp;rft.isbn=0-00-720660-7&amp;rft.au=Steve+Wright&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFactoid\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Dion Smythe (2007). \"A Whiter Shade of Pale: Issues and Opportunities in Prosopography\". Unit for Prosopographical Research, Linacre College, University of Oxford. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-1-900934-12-1\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-1-900934-12-1\">978-1-900934-12-1</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=A+Whiter+Shade+of+Pale%3A+Issues+and+Opportunities+in+Prosopography&amp;rft.date=2007&amp;rft.isbn=978-1-900934-12-1&amp;rft.au=Dion+Smythe&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AFactoid\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Brians, Paul (2003). <i>Common Errors in English Usage</i>. William James &amp; Company. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"Internati